1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,830
Hinata.

2
00:00:00,830 --> 00:00:02,130
Kamiki-san?

3
00:00:02,130 --> 00:00:04,340
Working late tonight?

4
00:00:04,340 --> 00:00:08,300
Yes, I want to catch up
with everyone as soon as possible.

5
00:00:08,300 --> 00:00:09,590
So I need to put in some extra effort.

6
00:00:09,590 --> 00:00:11,180
That's very admirable.

7
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:16,980
Well, that's only part of it.

8
00:00:16,980 --> 00:00:21,150
My brother went camping today,
so there's no one at home.

9
00:00:21,150 --> 00:00:22,110
Camping on a weekday?

10
00:00:22,110 --> 00:00:24,070
He's in grad school.

11
00:00:25,610 --> 00:00:28,490
Must be nice to be a student.

12
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:33,580
Actually, he originally asked me
to go with him.

13
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:38,120
So you're staying here because you're lonely?

14
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:39,580
No, that's not it!

15
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:42,380
I really just have work to finish.

16
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:45,920
I keep making mistakes at work,

17
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:48,720
and causing trouble for everyone.

18
00:00:48,720 --> 00:00:51,180
I want to pull my own weight soon,

19
00:00:51,180 --> 00:00:54,140
so I have to work even harder.

20
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,970
Alright, I get it.

21
00:00:56,970 --> 00:00:58,020
Let me help you.

22
00:00:58,020 --> 00:00:59,890
Really? Are you sure?

23
00:00:59,890 --> 00:01:02,650
Where are you at right now?

24
00:01:02,650 --> 00:01:07,360
I'm working on the presentation
for PP Industries next week.

25
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,650
But I'm not sure how to draft the budget.

26
00:01:10,900 --> 00:01:15,740
I did a similar proposal before.

27
00:01:15,740 --> 00:01:18,750
You can use it as a reference.

28
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:22,750
Wow, this is amazing and so detailed.

29
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:26,000
Thank you so much.

30
00:01:27,630 --> 00:01:30,630
With such a hardworking younger brother,

31
00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:33,590
how could he bear to leave you behind?

32
00:01:33,970 --> 00:01:35,640
Huh?
